[
    {
        "text": "He saw the universal capacity to carry out harms of great magnitude.",
        "startTime": 4361,
        "endTime": 10114,
        "slowStartTime": 6692,
        "slowEndTime": 15396
    },
    {
        "text": "Lemkin knew that no one was safe.",
        "startTime": 11211,
        "endTime": 13225,
        "slowStartTime": 16966,
        "slowEndTime": 20062
    },
    {
        "text": "Raphael Lemkin was a Polish Jew and when Hitler invaded Poland,...",
        "startTime": 16327,
        "endTime": 20915,
        "slowStartTime": 24640,
        "slowEndTime": 31598
    },
    {
        "text": "...47 members of his family were herded up and killed.",
        "startTime": 21033,
        "endTime": 24084,
        "slowStartTime": 31700,
        "slowEndTime": 36351
    },
    {
        "text": "I became interested in terrible suffering because it happened so many times.",
        "startTime": 24789,
        "endTime": 28713,
        "slowStartTime": 37333,
        "slowEndTime": 43294
    },
    {
        "text": "I said to myself, \"I'm going to do something about it.\"",
        "startTime": 29113,
        "endTime": 31743,
        "slowStartTime": 43819,
        "slowEndTime": 47839
    },
    {
        "text": "Lemkin came up with a new idea to transform these massacres into a crime.",
        "startTime": 33977,
        "endTime": 37533,
        "slowStartTime": 51115,
        "slowEndTime": 56524
    },
    {
        "text": "Something clicked in him.",
        "startTime": 38707,
        "endTime": 39887,
        "slowStartTime": 58211,
        "slowEndTime": 60056
    },
    {
        "text": "Maybe if I had a better word,...",
        "startTime": 40225,
        "endTime": 42165,
        "slowStartTime": 60487,
        "slowEndTime": 63472
    },
    {
        "text": "...maybe then, governments would ban the mass murder of civilians.",
        "startTime": 42475,
        "endTime": 46328,
        "slowStartTime": 63862,
        "slowEndTime": 69717
    },
    {
        "text": "Genocide.",
        "startTime": 47397,
        "endTime": 47927,
        "slowStartTime": 71245,
        "slowEndTime": 72115
    },
    {
        "text": "So, he has a word.",
        "startTime": 48790,
        "endTime": 49753,
        "slowStartTime": 73335,
        "slowEndTime": 74855
    },
    {
        "text": "Now what?",
        "startTime": 50135,
        "endTime": 50737,
        "slowStartTime": 75352,
        "slowEndTime": 76331
    },
    {
        "text": "How did one little guy go about trying to reform the world?",
        "startTime": 52217,
        "endTime": 56347,
        "slowStartTime": 78475,
        "slowEndTime": 84746
    },
    {
        "text": "Lemkin turned himself into a one-man lobbying machine.",
        "startTime": 56564,
        "endTime": 59898,
        "slowStartTime": 84996,
        "slowEndTime": 90072
    },
    {
        "text": "The convention was adopted by unanimous fashion.",
        "startTime": 60563,
        "endTime": 63532,
        "slowStartTime": 90994,
        "slowEndTime": 95523
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's open up the world and let light and knowledge come in.",
        "startTime": 63655,
        "endTime": 66854,
        "slowStartTime": 95633,
        "slowEndTime": 100506
    },
    {
        "text": "Today is a milestone.",
        "startTime": 68966,
        "endTime": 70304,
        "slowStartTime": 103599,
        "slowEndTime": 105681
    },
    {
        "text": "No criminal court has filed genocide charges against the President of Sudan.",
        "startTime": 70479,
        "endTime": 74222,
        "slowStartTime": 105868,
        "slowEndTime": 111558
    },
    {
        "text": "This monstrous conflict has to come to an end.",
        "startTime": 74749,
        "endTime": 77111,
        "slowStartTime": 112273,
        "slowEndTime": 115892
    },
    {
        "text": "I am myself a survivor of genocide.",
        "startTime": 77965,
        "endTime": 79893,
        "slowStartTime": 117098,
        "slowEndTime": 120065
    },
    {
        "text": "These people are waiting for our protection.",
        "startTime": 81446,
        "endTime": 83146,
        "slowStartTime": 122319,
        "slowEndTime": 124944
    },
    {
        "text": "We don't need to wait until he's finished his work.",
        "startTime": 83454,
        "endTime": 85455,
        "slowStartTime": 125331,
        "slowEndTime": 128407
    },
    {
        "text": "That was Lemkin's point,...",
        "startTime": 86834,
        "endTime": 87883,
        "slowStartTime": 130401,
        "slowEndTime": 132050
    },
    {
        "text": "...that perpetrators will be watched, that they will be accountable.",
        "startTime": 88471,
        "endTime": 91336,
        "slowStartTime": 132857,
        "slowEndTime": 137229
    },
    {
        "text": "I think, at a certain time, we have to stop and say,...",
        "startTime": 94045,
        "endTime": 96703,
        "slowStartTime": 141217,
        "slowEndTime": 145279
    },
    {
        "text": "\"We stop here.\"",
        "startTime": 97219,
        "endTime": 97919,
        "slowStartTime": 145978,
        "slowEndTime": 147103
    },
    {
        "text": "The law is the difference between life or death.",
        "startTime": 101279,
        "endTime": 103297,
        "slowStartTime": 152068,
        "slowEndTime": 155171
    },
    {
        "text": "I cannot fail.",
        "startTime": 104823,
        "endTime": 105509,
        "slowStartTime": 157384,
        "slowEndTime": 158489
    },
    {
        "text": "We cannot fail.",
        "startTime": 105741,
        "endTime": 106316,
        "slowStartTime": 158761,
        "slowEndTime": 159699
    },
    {
        "text": "I always think about the privilege of getting to try,...",
        "startTime": 111796,
        "endTime": 115179,
        "slowStartTime": 167844,
        "slowEndTime": 172994
    },
    {
        "text": "...just to try.",
        "startTime": 115651,
        "endTime": 116311,
        "slowStartTime": 173627,
        "slowEndTime": 174692
    }
]